COMMANDS TO LEARN
─────────────────
  g o     Toggle selected diff hunks (show/hide inline diff)
  g O     Toggle staged status
  g u     Stage current hunk and jump to next
  g U     Unstage current hunk and jump to next
  g R     Git restore (discard changes in hunk)

NOTE: These are ZED-SPECIFIC additions — not in native Helix!

INSTRUCTIONS
────────────
  These git commands work on diff hunks in modified files.
  Fill in the workflow steps below.

  This is a conceptual exercise — practice these in a real
  git repository to see them in action.

────────────────────────── PRACTICE ──────────────────────────────

